/**
 * cli/dump_runners: IR-dump subcommand runners.
 *
 * Covers nexus ast / hir / lir / types / caps subcommands. Each runner
 * runs a slimmed pipeline (parse → HIR → optional MIR+LIR) and prints
 * the IR as text or JSON. No codegen.
 */

